prop_args.props[DUMMY_PROP_NM] = pa.Prop(lowval=lowval, hival=hival, atype=
    pa.INT)
assert prop_args._answer_within_bounds(prop_nm=DUMMY_PROP_NM, typed_answer=
    test_val) == expected
pytest.mark.parametrize('lowval, test_val, hival, expected', [(None, 7,
    None, True), (None, -5, 10, True), (0, 99, None, True), (0, 7, 10, True
    ), (0, 77, 10, False), (0, -5, 10, False)])
